dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Oneida County, Wisconsin in YE2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Oneida_Roads_YE2016.gdb.[The roads feature class contains information regarding centerlines of public and private roads in the county. The roads contain geocoding information as well as the road name. Some road centerlines have been GPS'd to insure their accuracy while others were digitized from aerial photography. State and Federal highways are included in this dataset, while some counties choose to digitize or represent divided highways this is not the case in this dataset.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://oneida.ncwrpc.info/This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
